|----------|---------|----------|
| `validation.hbs` | Generate validation rules for each model | ✅ |
| `authorize.hbs` | Generate authorization logic for routes | ✅ |
| `router.hbs` | Generate full router with validation and authorization | ✅ |
| `authorize.js` | Centralized authorization logic | ✅ |
| `validate.js` | Centralized validation logic | ✅ |

